      "solution": "import sys\nimport math\n\n# Initialization\nw, h, g = map(int, input().split())\n\n# Racket Grid\nprint(\"o\"*(w*2+1))\nfor y in range(h):\n  print(end=\"o \")\n  for x in range(w-1):\n    print(end=\"| \")\n  print(end=\"o\")\n  print()\n  if y!=h-1:\n    print(end=\"o-\")\n    for x in range(w-1):\n      print(end=\"+-\")\n    print(end=\"o\")\n    print()\nprint(\"o\"*(w*2+1))\n\n# Grip\nfor i in range(g):\n  if i==g-1:\n    print(\" \"*(w-1)+\"|_|\")\n  else:\n    print(\" \"*(w-1)+\"| |\")",
